title: Print, "Female Head, Facing Front", 1935
description: The ovoid face is framed by shoulder-length, wavy hair. Straight brows, closed eyes, nose tip and fleshy mouth and sunken cheeks are the salient facial features.

tombstone.epitaph:
Print, "Female Head, Facing Front", 1935.
1935. 27 x 23.5 cm (10 5/8 x 9 1/4 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-150.
